佢同我講, 不如你試下食煙呀, 次次都係得我食. 跟住我話, 我睇住你好開心咁食煙經已夠架啦. <br />\n<br />\n再跟住佢講,  一齊食應該會開心d架<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟住我講, 咁呀, 不如大家食埋同一支煙啦<br />\n<br />\n之後, 每次拍拖, 都係大家share同一支煙"},{"pid":"c3556e729dc0e0fc763025506cba312b607cf83e","tid":428121,"uid":46798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T07:50:19.000Z","msg":"細個貪玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 考試個陣食起碼可以有幾分鐘可以懶係有重要野做放鬆一陣<br />\n不過而家戒咗就黎4年lu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ae469a8f13c70d7b80733559e99b695cd0b37e8","tid":428121,"uid":46798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T07:51:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個貪玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 考試<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">溫書</span>個陣食起碼可以有幾分鐘可以懶係有重要野做放鬆一陣<br />\n不過而家戒咗就黎4年lu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"2db09d638181012f6e1114dceacaa0033c9ca16d","tid":428121,"uid":38017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T07:52:29.000Z","msg":"中學食左一淡就冇食過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完全唔知食黎為乜"},{"pid":"bea519eaa065b11d55b0331aecc104d8677d2974","tid":428121,"uid":75753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T10:02:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食初戀分手食第一支，果陣12歲...</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 12歲"},{"pid":"4b68dc4e5d3a554bbf483f77170bbbe864e98157","tid":428121,"uid":75753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T10:03:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我唔食煙, 但我期望既第一支煙係同煙鏟女朋友一齊食<br />\n<br />\n首先, 希望溝到靚女煙鏟<br />\n<br />\n每次拍拖, 佢都會食好多煙, 所以我都會食佢大量既二手煙<br />\n<br />\n突然有一次, 我幫完佢點煙之後, 佢同我講, 不如你試下食煙呀, 次次都係得我食. 跟住我話, 我睇住你好開心咁食煙經已夠架啦. <br />\n<br />\n再跟住佢講,  一齊食應該會開心d架<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟住我講, 咁呀, 不如大家食埋同一支煙啦<br />\n<br />\n之後, 每次拍拖, 都係大家share同一支煙</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1dd7fab10753e62f6d4ddb0bc4a54b23ac5f6d7","tid":428121,"uid":75753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T10:04:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>為條初戀毀自己健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大把嘢可以令你唔諗啦<br />\neg做運動,識朋友,同班fd周圍玩<br />\n食咗真係翻唔到轉頭</blockquote><br />\n有做運動呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都有同fd周圍玩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但夜晚一個人既時候有時都係會無啦啦又諗返起以前既嘢"},{"pid":"d19a485698d35d4461410c9a3536427a064d9ee8","tid":428121,"uid":62167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T10:12:50.000Z","msg":"地下執到 自來煙唔食走寶<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但陣味同我之後食的煙完全唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb90b2525cc3e034930814efbbb36fa93a2e9b61","tid":428121,"uid":127116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T11:01:01.000Z","msg":"係人生第一個真正鐘意既人教我食既第一枝煙<br />\n雖然而家對個人已經無哂感覺<br />\n但個日既畫面我應該呢世都會記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f5b158665b19243130d4f5143707efd128c280d","tid":428121,"uid":542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T11:04:08.000Z","msg":"小學好奇試左一枝<br />\n好難食又臭"},{"pid":"8f1cffeab9940e7e28bed7e0204e7278b3027f6a","tid":428121,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T11:23:14.000Z","msg":"小學偷老豆啲煙試 到之後失戀成日食 前排戒咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b29238f8bfa682d7654685e866fc0c9